+## 1. Current Repository State (v0.2.0)
+
+As of v0.2.0, the repository contains:
+
+- Working extraction scripts for raw and annual-mean UM outputs
+- Core carbon- and soil-related diagnostic logic
+- Plotting utilities for time series and summary diagnostics
+- Example notebooks demonstrating end-to-end workflows
+
+The following are considered **functionally correct but structurally provisional**:
+
+- analysis.py
+- plot.py
+- ad-hoc path discovery logic in scripts/
+
+These files may be refactored but must not lose scientific functionality.
+
